{
  "texts": [
    "Stage 2 introduces Discrete Wavelet Transform (DWT) to enhance these features, enabling the system to concentrate on crucial elements.",
    "In the third stage, the approach employs these features to classify the images, frames, or segments into one of three categories: human, animal, or neither.",
    "The Ensemble Model Architecture (DEV-22 + DWT + SVM).",
    "multiclass support vector machine (SVM) assists in conducting the final classification.",
    "In the final stage of the pipeline, the U-Net network uses semantic segmentation to pinpoint the precise location of malignant polyps in the images."
  ]
}